 Because we have more particles here 

00:00:30.723 --> 00:00:31.795
 and they bounce around 

00:00:31.795 --> 00:00:33.735
 in different random directions, 

00:00:33.735 --> 00:00:35.095
 there is a greater likelihood that particles will move 

00:00:35.095 --> 00:00:38.230
