 these large yellow particles. 

00:01:02.179 --> 00:01:04.199
 We see the concentration gradient of these particles 

00:01:04.199 --> 00:01:06.370
 is in the opposite direction. 

00:01:06.370 --> 00:01:08.276
 We have low concentration, 

