 The particles simply bounce randomly 

00:02:00.142 --> 00:02:01.854
 and when in the beginning 

00:02:01.854 --> 00:02:03.986
 we have a situation like this, there is no chance 

00:02:03.986 --> 00:02:07.485
 yellow particles to move from left to right, 

00:02:07.485 --> 00:02:09.357
 because there are no yellow particles here. 

