 They will continue to do so, 

00:02:19.743 --> 00:02:21.830
 until they reach a stable configuration, 

00:02:21.830 --> 00:02:24.383
 where there is the same probability 

00:02:24.383 --> 00:02:27.042
 to move the particles from left to right and right to left. 

00:02:27.042 --> 00:02:29.306
 This will happen in both particle types. 

